'''Pierre de Villiers''' (born 26 July 1956) is a [[French people|French]] [[Army general (France)|army general]]. He has served as [[Chief of the Defence Staff (France)|Chief of the Defence Staff]] since 15 February 2014.<ref>[http://www.lemonde.fr/international/article/2014/01/15/le-general-pierre-de-villiers-prend-la-tete-de-l-etat-major-des-armees_4348111_3210.html Le général Pierre de Villiers prend la tête de l'état-major des armées], article de Nathalie Guibert sur ''Le Monde'' en date du 15 janvier 2014 (consulté le 26 mai 2014).</ref> His brother is the French politician [[Philippe de Villiers]].

